desc_short	-----								1861. The Civil War has been declared in the United States. Two clans are fighting: The abolitionist Union and the pro-slavery Confederates. NORTH vs SOUTH is inspired from THE BLUE COATS comic book. You'll relive the biggest events of this battle with Sergeant Chesterfield and Corporal Butch.							
developer									Microids								
